    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. The exterior shows its age with some fading on the clear coat, a few small door dings, and minor surface rust on the rear wheel arches. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows noticeable wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it has a slow oil drip and will likely need new brake pads and tires in the coming months. It\u2019s a solid, functional car that has been used regularly, but it is not a showpiece and is priced accordingly for its current state.",
