    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me and is still running like a champ! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect choice if you want something dependable without that brand-new price tag. I'm honestly a bit sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019ll make the next owner very happy. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The high-revving valvetrain benefits from a documented double-VANOS overhaul, and the chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement to maintain structural integrity under torque load. It features a factory M-variable limited-slip differential and a refreshed suspension setup utilizing polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in response. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical synchronization and compression across all cylinders remain within tight factory tolerances, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Engine runs well. Body shows minor wear. Interior is clean. Fully functional.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance and comfort. The exterior is finished in a timeless coat that still holds a deep, reflective gloss; while you might find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper from highway commuting, the body panels are straight and free of any significant dings or scratches. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, a testament to a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule\u2014I have kept full records of every oil change and fluid flush performed over the last three years. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains firm yet forgiving, providing a confident ride on both city streets and open roads. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with upholstery that shows very minimal wear. All electronic features, including the dual-zone climate control, premium sound system, and navigation, are fully functional. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes were recently inspected and serviced. This is a dependable, turn-key car ready for its next owner to enjoy without any immediate investment required.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer. Meticulously maintained and displaying consistent mechanical integrity, it offers an exceptional balance of performance and long-term value. With a documented service history and a well-preserved interior, this unit stands as a testament to responsible ownership and our dealership\u2019s rigorous standards for quality.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for over the years. It drives beautifully and still has that great look that\u2019ll turn heads in the driveway! Perfect for anyone who wants a dependable, high-quality ride without the 'brand new' sticker shock. I'd love for you to come by, check it out, and take it for a test drive!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen has had its rod bearings proactively replaced and throttle actuators serviced, addressing the platform's primary failure points. The chassis remains taut with a recent refresh of the multi-link rear suspension and EDC dampers. Power is delivered through a healthy M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal traction under load. The engine pulls strongly to its 8400 RPM redline with a linear power band and no Vanos noise. A true driver's car with the mechanical pedigree to match its performance heritage.",
